                    <msContents n="1">
                        <!--increment n attribute for ms containing multiple ms items-->
                        <summary>
                            A modern manuscript of the <title xml:lang="san" type="general">Dvāviṃśatyavadānakathā</title>. 
                            This manuscript has been used by M. Okada for her edition (1993), where it is given the siglum C. 
                            According to the <term xml:lang="lat">stemma codicum</term> provided in the edition, 
                            this manuscript is the only witness of one distinct branch of the manuscript tradition, and is very near to the archetype.
                        </summary>
                        
